<br>
1. targetted AE spells - you aim at a target, the spell radiates out from the target.  It hits up to 4 NPCs, which is why wizards and druids &quot;QUAD kite&quot; not triple kite or something.  Four at a time.  The first good one a wizard gets is circle of force.  Wizard snare is also an AE spell and also snares up to 4 mobs around whatever is targetted.  I think enchanter area mez is like this one.  These AEs will not affect group members (unless you're standing in a PvP arena) but WILL affect the caster so you have to be careful to have high resists or to stay out of range.<br>
<br>
